Class LazyExecutionLineageNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.wayang.core.platform.lineage.LazyExecutionLineageNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChannelLineageNode, ExecutionLineageNode
    public abstract class LazyExecutionLineageNode
extends java.lang.Object
    A node wraps a ChannelInstance and keeps track of predecessor nodes.
